{
  "video_id": "H2QxFM9y0tY",
  "title": "The disarming case to act right now on climate change | Greta Thunberg",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Akinori Oyama Reviewer: Michael Rieken"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13341.0,
      "end_time": 16308.0,
      "text": "When I was about eight years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16308.0,
      "end_time": 20550.0,
      "text": "I first heard about something called climate change or global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21619.0,
      "end_time": 26189.0,
      "text": "Apparently, that was something humans have created by our way of living."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27222.0,
      "end_time": 30839.0,
      "text": "I was told to turn off the lights to save energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31880.0,
      "end_time": 34459.0,
      "text": "and to recycle paper to save resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36268.0,
      "end_time": 39790.0,
      "text": "I remember thinking that it was very strange"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39309.0,
      "end_time": 43190.0,
      "text": "that humans, who are an animal species among others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43190.0,
      "end_time": 47198.0,
      "text": "could be capable of changing the Earth&#39;s climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 48900.0,
      "end_time": 51561.0,
      "text": "Because if we were, and if it was really happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 51836.0,
      "end_time": 54739.0,
      "text": "we wouldn&#39;t be talking about anything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 55720.0,
      "end_time": 60000.0,
      "text": "As soon as you&#39;d turn on the TV, everything would be about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 60508.0,
      "end_time": 63541.0,
      "text": "Headlines, radio, newspapers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 63849.0,
      "end_time": 66690.0,
      "text": "you would never read or hear about anything else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 67180.0,
      "end_time": 69719.0,
      "text": "as if there was a world war going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 70838.0,
      "end_time": 73360.0,
      "text": "But no one ever talked about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 74130.0,
      "end_time": 80154.0,
      "text": "If burning fossil fuels was so bad that it threatened our very existence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 80649.0,
      "end_time": 83278.0,
      "text": "how could we just continue like before?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 84263.0,
      "end_time": 86498.0,
      "text": "Why were there no restrictions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 87300.0,
      "end_time": 89320.0,
      "text": "Why wasn&#39;t it made illegal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 90921.0,
      "end_time": 93891.0,
      "text": "To me, that did not add up."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 94288.0,
      "end_time": 96297.0,
      "text": "It was too unreal."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 98401.0,
      "end_time": 100978.0,
      "text": "So when I was 11, I became ill."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 101250.0,
      "end_time": 103420.0,
      "text": "I fell into depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 103319.0,
      "end_time": 104613.0,
      "text": "I stopped talking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 104998.0,
      "end_time": 106487.0,
      "text": "and I stopped eating."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 107699.0,
      "end_time": 111488.0,
      "text": "In two months, I lost about 10 kilos of weight."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 112889.0,
      "end_time": 116800.0,
      "text": "Later on, I was diagnosed with Asperger syndrome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 116319.0,
      "end_time": 119289.0,
      "text": "OCD and selective mutism."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 120189.0,
      "end_time": 123759.0,
      "text": "That basically means I only speak when I think it&#39;s necessary -"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123760.0,
      "end_time": 125670.0,
      "text": "now is one of those moments."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 125670.0,
      "end_time": 129258.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 135908.0,
      "end_time": 138290.0,
      "text": "For those of us who are on the spectrum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 138290.0,
      "end_time": 140857.0,
      "text": "almost everything is black or white."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 141564.0,
      "end_time": 143233.0,
      "text": "We aren&#39;t very good at lying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143234.0,
      "end_time": 146598.0,
      "text": "and we usually don&#39;t enjoy participating in this social game"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 146598.0,
      "end_time": 149153.0,
      "text": "that the rest of you seem so fond of."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 149153.0,
      "end_time": 150423.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 150688.0,
      "end_time": 153750.0,
      "text": "I think in many ways that we autistic are the normal ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 154410.0,
      "end_time": 156368.0,
      "text": "and the rest of the people are pretty strange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 156368.0,
      "end_time": 157561.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 157561.0,
      "end_time": 160509.0,
      "text": "especially when it comes to the sustainability crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 160800.0,
      "end_time": 164525.0,
      "text": "where everyone keeps saying climate change is an existential threat"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 164925.0,
      "end_time": 167136.0,
      "text": "and the most important issue of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 167534.0,
      "end_time": 170820.0,
      "text": "and yet they just carry on like before."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 171631.0,
      "end_time": 173396.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t understand that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 173699.0,
      "end_time": 176198.0,
      "text": "because if the emissions have to stop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 176447.0,
      "end_time": 178579.0,
      "text": "then we must stop the emissions."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 179194.0,
      "end_time": 181180.0,
      "text": "To me that is black or white."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 181698.0,
      "end_time": 184460.0,
      "text": "There are no gray areas when it comes to survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 184830.0,
      "end_time": 187781.0,
      "text": "Either we go on as a civilization or we don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 188646.0,
      "end_time": 190939.0,
      "text": "We have to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 192160.0,
      "end_time": 195950.0,
      "text": "Rich countries like Sweden need to start reducing emissions"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 195950.0,
      "end_time": 199230.0,
      "text": "by at least 15 percent every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 200199.0,
      "end_time": 204119.0,
      "text": "And that is so that we can stay below a two-degree warming target."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 204821.0,
      "end_time": 208273.0,
      "text": "Yet, as the IPCC have recently demonstrated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 209250.0,
      "end_time": 212116.0,
      "text": "aiming instead for 1.5 degrees Celsius"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 212362.0,
      "end_time": 215302.0,
      "text": "would significantly reduce the climate impacts."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 215928.0,
      "end_time": 219798.0,
      "text": "But we can only imagine what that means for reducing emissions."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 220897.0,
      "end_time": 223600.0,
      "text": "You would think the media and every one of our leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 223607.0,
      "end_time": 225607.0,
      "text": "would be talking about nothing else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 225897.0,
      "end_time": 228167.0,
      "text": "but they never even mention it."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 229400.0,
      "end_time": 230733.0,
      "text": "Nor does anyone ever mention"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230739.0,
      "end_time": 233859.0,
      "text": "the greenhouse gases already locked in the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 234340.0,
      "end_time": 237115.0,
      "text": "Nor that air pollution is hiding a warming"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 237455.0,
      "end_time": 240128.0,
      "text": "so that when we stop burning fossil fuels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 240416.0,
      "end_time": 242617.0,
      "text": "we already have an extra level of warming"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 242864.0,
      "end_time": 247314.0,
      "text": "perhaps as high as 0.5 to 1.1 degrees Celsius."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 249720.0,
      "end_time": 251624.0,
      "text": "Furthermore does hardly anyone speak about the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 251624.0,
      "end_time": 255176.0,
      "text": "that we are in the midst of the sixth mass extinction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 255765.0,
      "end_time": 260685.0,
      "text": "with up to 200 species going extinct every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 262178.0,
      "end_time": 265819.0,
      "text": "that the extinction rate today"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 265819.0,
      "end_time": 269619.0,
      "text": "is between 1,000 and 10,000 times higher"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 269619.0,
      "end_time": 271848.0,
      "text": "than what is seen as normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 274516.0,
      "end_time": 279879.0,
      "text": "Nor does hardly anyone ever speak about the aspect of equity or climate justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 280250.0,
      "end_time": 283227.0,
      "text": "clearly stated everywhere in the Paris Agreement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 283614.0,
      "end_time": 287849.0,
      "text": "which is absolutely necessary to make it work on a global scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 289486.0,
      "end_time": 291342.0,
      "text": "That means that rich countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 291342.0,
      "end_time": 295279.0,
      "text": "need to get down to zero emissions within 6 to 12 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 296650.0,
      "end_time": 298337.0,
      "text": "with today&#39;s emission speed."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 300190.0,
      "end_time": 302330.0,
      "text": "And that is so that people in poorer countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 302330.0,
      "end_time": 304990.0,
      "text": "can have a chance to heighten their standard of living"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 304990.0,
      "end_time": 308558.0,
      "text": "by building some of the infrastructure that we have already built,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 308863.0,
      "end_time": 311911.0,
      "text": "such as roads, schools, hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 311911.0,
      "end_time": 314960.0,
      "text": "clean drinking water, electricity, and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 315707.0,
      "end_time": 320299.0,
      "text": "Because how can we expect countries like India or Nigeria"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 320303.0,
      "end_time": 322180.0,
      "text": "to care about the climate crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 322185.0,
      "end_time": 327190.0,
      "text": "if we who already have everything don&#39;t care even a second about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 327190.0,
      "end_time": 330480.0,
      "text": "or our actual commitments to the Paris Agreement?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 332449.0,
      "end_time": 336527.0,
      "text": "So, why are we not reducing our emissions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 337611.0,
      "end_time": 340909.0,
      "text": "Why are they in fact still increasing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 341820.0,
      "end_time": 345310.0,
      "text": "Are we knowingly causing a mass extinction?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 345738.0,
      "end_time": 347429.0,
      "text": "Are we evil?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 349118.0,
      "end_time": 351299.0,
      "text": "No, of course not."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 351700.0,
      "end_time": 353329.0,
      "text": "People keep doing what they do"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 353329.0,
      "end_time": 355969.0,
      "text": "because the vast majority doesn&#39;t have a clue"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 355969.0,
      "end_time": 359722.0,
      "text": "about the actual consequences of our everyday life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 360474.0,
      "end_time": 363449.0,
      "text": "and they don&#39;t know that rapid change is required."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 364480.0,
      "end_time": 368446.0,
      "text": "We all think we know, and we all think everybody knows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 368447.0,
      "end_time": 370200.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 370708.0,
      "end_time": 372339.0,
      "text": "Because how could we?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 374474.0,
      "end_time": 376459.0,
      "text": "If there really was a crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 376696.0,
      "end_time": 379583.0,
      "text": "and if this crisis was caused by our emissions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 380000.0,
      "end_time": 382277.0,
      "text": "you would at least see some signs."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 383480.0,
      "end_time": 386918.0,
      "text": "Not just flooded cities, tens of thousands of dead people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 387166.0,
      "end_time": 391100.0,
      "text": "and whole nations leveled to piles of torn down buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 391904.0,
      "end_time": 394183.0,
      "text": "You would see some restrictions."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 394616.0,
      "end_time": 396300.0,
      "text": "But no."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 396774.0,
      "end_time": 398570.0,
      "text": "And no one talks about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 400359.0,
      "end_time": 406320.0,
      "text": "There are no emergency meetings, no headlines, no breaking news."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 406659.0,
      "end_time": 409645.0,
      "text": "No one is acting as if we were in a crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 410309.0,
      "end_time": 414129.0,
      "text": "Even most climate scientists or green politicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 414399.0,
      "end_time": 418130.0,
      "text": "keep on flying around the world, eating meat and dairy."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 422267.0,
      "end_time": 428570.0,
      "text": "If I live to be 100, I will be alive in the year 2103."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 429738.0,
      "end_time": 435181.0,
      "text": "When you think about the future today, you don&#39;t think beyond the year 2050."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 436178.0,
      "end_time": 440992.0,
      "text": "By then, I will, in the best case, not even have lived half of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 442319.0,
      "end_time": 443969.0,
      "text": "What happens next?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 445559.0,
      "end_time": 451590.0,
      "text": "The year 2078, I will celebrate my 75th birthday."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 452450.0,
      "end_time": 457460.0,
      "text": "If I have children or grandchildren, maybe they will spend that day with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 458682.0,
      "end_time": 460953.0,
      "text": "Maybe they will ask me about you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 461384.0,
      "end_time": 464893.0,
      "text": "the people who were around, back in 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 466786.0,
      "end_time": 469268.0,
      "text": "Maybe they will ask why you didn&#39;t do anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 469830.0,
      "end_time": 472260.0,
      "text": "while there still was time to act."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 473890.0,
      "end_time": 478268.0,
      "text": "What we do or don&#39;t do right now will affect my entire life"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 478268.0,
      "end_time": 481470.0,
      "text": "and the lives of my children and grandchildren."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 481960.0,
      "end_time": 484555.0,
      "text": "What we do or don&#39;t do right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 484562.0,
      "end_time": 488681.0,
      "text": "me and my generation can&#39;t undo in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 492169.0,
      "end_time": 495340.0,
      "text": "So when school started in August of this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 495340.0,
      "end_time": 497594.0,
      "text": "I decided that this was enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 498830.0,
      "end_time": 502150.0,
      "text": "I set myself down on the ground outside the Swedish parliament."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 502510.0,
      "end_time": 504928.0,
      "text": "I school striked for the climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 506677.0,
      "end_time": 509755.0,
      "text": "Some people say that I should be in school instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 510269.0,
      "end_time": 513929.0,
      "text": "Some people say that I should study to become a climate scientist"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 513929.0,
      "end_time": 517223.0,
      "text": "so that I can \"solve the climate crisis.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 518868.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521631.00000000006,
      "text": "But the climate crisis has already been solved."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 522400.0,
      "end_time": 525367.0,
      "text": "We already have all the facts and solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 525920.0,
      "end_time": 528818.0,
      "text": "All we have to do is to wake up and change."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 530100.0,
      "end_time": 534729.0,
      "text": "And why should I be studying for a future that soon will be no more"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 534839.0,
      "end_time": 538799.0,
      "text": "when no one is doing anything whatsoever to save that future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 539859.0,
      "end_time": 543279.0,
      "text": "And what is the point of learning facts in the school system"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 543943.0,
      "end_time": 545901.0,
      "text": "when the most important facts"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 545902.0,
      "end_time": 549349.0,
      "text": "given by the finest science of that same school system"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 549620.0,
      "end_time": 553629.0,
      "text": "clearly means nothing to our politicians and our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 555588.0,
      "end_time": 558647.0,
      "text": "Some people say that Sweden is just a small country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 558869.0,
      "end_time": 561499.0,
      "text": "and that it doesn&#39;t matter what we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 561901.0,
      "end_time": 566179.0,
      "text": "but I think that if a few children can get headlines all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 566179.0,
      "end_time": 568646.0,
      "text": "just by not coming to school for a few weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 569770.0,
      "end_time": 572108.0,
      "text": "imagine what we could all do together if you wanted to."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 572108.0,
      "end_time": 575524.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 576500.0,
      "end_time": 579170.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;re almost at the end of my talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 581890.0,
      "end_time": 586380.0,
      "text": "and this is where people usually start talking about hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 586960.0,
      "end_time": 591412.0,
      "text": "solar panels, wind power, circular economy, and so on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 592380.0,
      "end_time": 594418.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m not going to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 594751.0,
      "end_time": 599319.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve had 30 years of pep-talking and selling positive ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 599912.0,
      "end_time": 602199.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m sorry, but it doesn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 602909.0,
      "end_time": 604516.0,
      "text": "Because if it would have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 604521.0,
      "end_time": 606779.0,
      "text": "the emissions would have gone down by now."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 606779.0,
      "end_time": 608432.0,
      "text": "They haven&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 609472.0,
      "end_time": 611920.0,
      "text": "And yes, we do need hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 612580.0,
      "end_time": 614189.0,
      "text": "of course we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 614649.0,
      "end_time": 618469.0,
      "text": "But the one thing we need more than hope is action."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 619400.0,
      "end_time": 622183.0,
      "text": "Once we start to act, hope is everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 623720.0,
      "end_time": 625960.0,
      "text": "So instead of looking for hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 625960.0,
      "end_time": 627820.0,
      "text": "look for action."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 628510.0,
      "end_time": 632519.0,
      "text": "Then, and only then, hope will come."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 634561.0,
      "end_time": 641450.0,
      "text": "Today, we use 100 million barrels of oil every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 641970.0,
      "end_time": 644221.0,
      "text": "There are no politics to change that."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 645148.0,
      "end_time": 647750.0,
      "text": "There are no rules to keep that oil in the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 649358.0,
      "end_time": 652395.0,
      "text": "So we can&#39;t save the world by playing by the rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 652990.0,
      "end_time": 655570.0,
      "text": "because the rules have to be changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 656199.0,
      "end_time": 658205.0,
      "text": "Everything needs to change --"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 658676.0,
      "end_time": 660540.0,
      "text": "and it has to start today."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 661900.0,
      "end_time": 662148.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 662148.0,
      "end_time": 665497.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}